  m_Name: NeighborJournal_05
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 22
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #5 \u2014 Ch\xFA Ba ti\u1EC7m t\u1EA1p h\xF3a"
  category: 3
  content: "Kho \u0111\xE3 c\u1EA1n s\u1EA1ch t\u1EEB h\xF4m qua. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
    ta gi\xE0nh gi\u1EADt nhau t\u1EEBng g\xF3i m\xEC, t\u1EEBng lon c\xE1. T\xF4i
    kh\xF4ng tr\xE1ch h\u1ECD, ai c\u0169ng s\u1EE3. C\u1EA3nh s\xE1t \u0111\u1EBFn
    canh nh\u01B0ng r\u1ED3i ch\xEDnh c\u1EA3nh s\xE1t c\u0169ng b\u1ECF \u0111i.
    \u0110\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i m\u1EA5y th\xF9ng n\u01B0\u1EDBc kho sau qu\u1EA7y, ai
    c\u1EA7n th\xEC l\u1EA5y. C\u1EEDa ti\u1EC7m m\u1EDF c\u1EEDa cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng.
    Ch\xFAc may m\u1EAFn."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
